• Creating various reports using Pentaho Report Designer.
• Design the reports according to Clients requirement.
• Used Embedded transformation to source the data from API for reports.
• Combine different reports into 1 report using sub-report in PRD.
• Testing the reports over core application.
• Deploying the reports on Reporting Server using Cicle CI.
• Upgrading Reporting System to support Excel, PDF, Cube, Xml, CSV files.
• Analyze & Trouble shoot problems in the existing reports.
• Menage the Jobs, Transformations and PRPT files using github.
